off this mountain.

03:43.520 --> 03:45.960
You reach that snowmobile
before I get to you.

03:46.080 --> 03:47.760
It's game over for me.

03:47.880 --> 03:49.920
You escape to civilization

03:50.040 --> 03:52.320
and I am left stranded to die
in the woods.

03:55.080 --> 03:57.640
As an elite sportsman,
I insist on true challenge.

03:57.720 --> 03:59.920
So, I'll be hunting you
with limited ammunition.

04:01.560 --> 04:04.280
My rifle holds three bullets
and those three bullets

04:04.400 --> 04:06.720
are the only ammunition
in my possession.

04:08.080 --> 04:10.000
I get three chances
to take you down.

04:10.120 --> 04:11.680
That's it.

04:11.800 --> 04:15.240
Use this to your advantage.
Strategize, Ava Bravo.

04:16.960 --> 04:18.880
Two pieces of advice.

04:19.000 --> 04:21.600
First, don't just run off
in a straight line.

04:21.720 --> 04:24.480
Second, if you're ransacking
the cabin right now

04:24.600 --> 04:28.040
looking for a weapon,
you are wasting precious time.

04:28.200 --> 04:29.200
There is nothing here

04:29.280 --> 04:31.160
that you could
possibly weaponize.

04:31.280 --> 04:34.520
All you can do
is start running.

04:34.680 --> 04:37.800
Because right now, Ava Bravo,
I'm down in the basement.

04:39.640 --> 04:41.440
And I'm about to come up.

04:43.560 --> 04:45.720
10 Mississippi...

04:45.840 --> 04:48.840
9 Mississippi...

04:49.000 --> 04:52.240
8 Mississippi...

04:52.320 --> 04:54.800
7 Mississippi...

04:54.960 --> 04:57.440
6 Mississippi...

04:57.560 --> 04:58.640
5...

06:15.320 --> 06:16.480
Ah.

09:08.560 --> 09:10.480
Son of a bitch.

09:44.240 --> 09:46.240
Five miles directly north
of this cabin,

09:46.360 --> 09:47.480
you'll find a lean-to.

09:48.800 --> 09:50.640
Inside is a shiny snowmobile.

13:05.880 --> 13:07.800
What the fuck is this?

13:12.960 --> 13:14.480
Fucking crazy man.

13:53.480 --> 13:57.440
I'm a survivor,
here, now and forever.

14:00.320 --> 14:02.160
I'm one with the Creator.

15:22.480 --> 15:26.160
I found it. There it is.

16:28.080 --> 16:29.320
Ah!

16:32.400 --> 16:34.400
Son of a bitch!

16:37.800 --> 16:38.800
Psych.

16:51.920 --> 16:53.200
Fucking traps.

16:55.360 --> 16:56.720
Son of a bitch!

17:52.720 --> 17:54.080
Where am I?

17:59.880 --> 18:02.960
There's nothing. There's nothing here.

18:27.800 --> 18:30.160
The son of a bitch brought me here.

18:30.240 --> 18:33.200
And the son of a bitch
will take me back.

19:58.600 --> 19:59.920
There it is.

20:03.960 --> 20:06.760
You can do it, you can do it. Come on.

21:15.640 --> 21:19.960
Don't worry, he's tied up.
Everything will be fine.

21:43.640 --> 21:44.640
Fuck!

21:47.280 --> 21:48.520
What'd you shoot out there?

21:52.040 --> 21:53.400
Figured you'd be hungry.

21:56.920 --> 21:57.960
More for me.

21:58.560 --> 21:59.920
Don't move!

22:09.080 --> 22:10.560
Well, here we are, Ava B.

22:11.720 --> 22:14.560
You are the first guest
to ever outsmart

22:14.680 --> 22:16.720
and outpower me.

22:17.520 --> 22:18.760
Where am I?

22:19.800 --> 22:21.240
Did my spikes get you at all?

22:23.200 --> 22:24.360
-Where am I?
-Hmm.

22:25.400 --> 22:26.920
No snowmobile out there, huh?

22:28.240 --> 22:30.600
Yeah, "psych."

22:30.720 --> 22:31.960
Hmm.

22:32.080 --> 22:33.080
Give me your phone.

22:33.840 --> 22:34.920
What phone?

22:35.040 --> 22:36.560
Give me your phone now.

22:36.640 --> 22:37.640
Didn't you listen?

22:37.760 --> 22:39.600
You have a fucking phone!

22:39.760 --> 22:42.000
You searched me and the cabin

22:42.160 --> 22:44.320
after you knocked my ass out, right?

22:44.400 --> 22:45.600
Did you find a phone?

22:48.560 --> 22:49.560
Okay.

22:50.840 --> 22:52.880
You tricked me
with your little footprints

22:53.000 --> 22:54.000
in the snow.

22:54.080 --> 22:55.080
Then you whacked me,

22:55.160 --> 22:57.120
you dragged my fat ass
down the stairs.

22:57.240 --> 22:58.800
You avoid the trap.

22:58.960 --> 23:00.120
You do all that.

23:01.000 --> 23:03.160
But then you cuff my hands
in front of me.

23:03.920 --> 23:05.280
I mean, in the front.

23:06.400 --> 23:08.360
Kind of a dumbass mistake.

23:08.400 --> 23:10.920
How about que te meto
este pinche rifle por el culo?

23:11.040 --> 23:13.440
Mm-mm, mm-mm.
English, por favor.

23:15.320 --> 23:17.840
'Cause this essentially makes me
a one-armed man.

23:17.920 --> 23:19.920
One armed-man
can still do a lot of damage.

23:22.960 --> 23:24.000
You know,

23:24.840 --> 23:27.720
I had an actual one-armed man
up here last winter.

23:29.600 --> 23:31.080
And he did great.

23:31.160 --> 23:33.400
Well, until he didn't.

23:34.760 --> 23:36.040
Where am I?

23:36.160 --> 23:37.600
Huh? Tell me

23:37.720 --> 23:40.520
how to get out of here
or I'm gonna fucking kill you.

23:40.720 --> 23:41.800
Nah.

23:43.040 --> 23:44.520
If you had killing in you,

23:44.600 --> 23:46.400
you would have done it
at the start.

23:46.440 --> 23:48.040
You don't know
what I have in me.

23:50.760 --> 23:55.040
At some point up that mountain,
you realized you need me

23:55.480 --> 23:56.480
to survive.

23:58.960 --> 23:59.960
Sit down.

24:02.360 --> 24:03.440
Let's not forget that.

24:03.560 --> 24:04.960
Sit down!

24:08.520 --> 24:10.320
No problemo, I say.

24:12.720 --> 24:15.000
You know, I had a tough choice
to make, too.

24:15.120 --> 24:16.440
I could've hidden.

24:16.560 --> 24:17.960
And bushwhacked you
when you came back.

24:18.080 --> 24:19.720
I could've choked ya
with these chains,

24:19.840 --> 24:20.880
but instead...

24:22.040 --> 24:23.720
I thought it would be nice
to talk.

24:24.960 --> 24:27.480
Have a little meal.
You know.

24:27.600 --> 24:29.280
Sorry, that it's just beans
and water.

24:29.440 --> 24:30.440
Well, I'm not interested.

24:30.520 --> 24:32.120
A Mexican
who doesn't want beans.

24:33.160 --> 24:35.480
-That's a first.
-Fuck you.

24:35.600 --> 24:37.040
So, what'd you shoot up there?

24:37.120 --> 24:39.560
Really, 'cause sound...
sound travels from miles up here

24:39.640 --> 24:41.800
so I knew
that you were still with us.

24:41.920 --> 24:43.760
Hmm? What was it?

24:47.080 --> 24:48.120
Okay.

24:49.080 --> 24:51.560
Doesn't matter.

24:51.720 --> 24:52.960
What does matter...

24:54.720 --> 24:56.400
is that you have now
squandered...

24:57.760 --> 24:59.680
...one precious round.

25:01.760 --> 25:03.360
You should just be careful

25:03.440 --> 25:05.080
that you don't waste
another shot.

25:08.720 --> 25:11.320
How about I waste a shot
right in your fucking face?

25:13.040 --> 25:15.760
Well, if you don't think
you need me to get out.

25:15.920 --> 25:17.880
Maybe, I just kill you

25:18.000 --> 25:20.320
and live in
this lovely cabin forever, hmm?

25:21.840 --> 25:23.080
Yeah, it is a nice escape.

25:25.320 --> 25:27.400
Gets a little lonely though.

25:27.520 --> 25:29.160
But you know
all about loneliness.

25:35.280 --> 25:38.520
Ava, I truly don't know

25:38.640 --> 25:41.280
what is gonna happen next
between us.

25:43.080 --> 25:45.720
And I just find that
so exhilarating.

25:48.880 --> 25:50.320
What's that?

25:50.400 --> 25:52.200
Fire off a couple of shots
for a test.

25:52.280 --> 25:53.520
Ha, ha, ha, ha.

25:53.600 --> 25:54.960
It's a bird.

25:55.080 --> 25:57.280
Hey, birds fly into buildings
sometimes.

25:59.040 --> 26:01.160
Because they make
dumbass mistakes, too.

26:14.320 --> 26:16.240
Comin' up on 18 months now, huh?

26:19.040 --> 26:21.200
And you haven't aged a day.

26:21.320 --> 26:22.600
You look great.

26:36.280 --> 26:39.080
You all have something
in common.

26:46.840 --> 26:48.680
-Yeah, you hunt survivors.
-Yes.

26:48.800 --> 26:50.800
-Real brave, fucking asshole.
-You know, if anybody other than

26:50.880 --> 26:52.600
you were doing this, they'd be
in a rubber room right now.

26:52.640 --> 26:54.000
No, you need to shut up.
Here's what's gonna happen.

26:54.080 --> 26:55.120
- Hey, you're amazing.
- You have to shut up.

26:55.240 --> 26:56.520
-I had this war hero up here.
-Here's what... No, no, no.

26:56.600 --> 26:57.600
I'm gonna do
something even worse.

26:57.720 --> 26:59.320
I need to know how I got here!

26:59.720 --> 27:01.440
There are no roads.

27:06.000 --> 27:07.640
First, there was a snowmobile.

27:16.600 --> 27:18.240
Then a little sled.

27:20.640 --> 27:22.080
Where is it?

27:22.200 --> 27:23.600
The snowmobile.

27:26.640 --> 27:28.640
Come on,
I'm not gonna answer that.

27:39.760 --> 27:41.760
Maybe you wanna rethink
that answer.

27:43.440 --> 27:45.200
If I die, you die.

27:52.840 --> 27:54.680
- Oh, what is it?
- Don't...

27:58.320 --> 28:00.280
What?

28:00.400 --> 28:02.320
I don't know. I swear to God.

28:08.280 --> 28:09.640
- Shoot him.
- What?

28:09.720 --> 28:11.600
Shoot him now.
Shoot him!

28:15.720 --> 28:17.880
-What the fuck is happening?
-In here.

28:17.960 --> 28:19.240
Where are you going?

28:19.360 --> 28:21.680
♪

28:30.360 --> 28:31.360
Where are you?

28:31.480 --> 28:33.840
Get into the light,
so I can see you.

28:33.960 --> 28:35.920
Do what I say when I say it.

28:37.280 --> 28:38.680
Or I'm gonna open the door.

28:38.720 --> 28:40.720
- Bullshit.
- Come on.

28:40.800 --> 28:42.920
I have nothing to lose.

28:43.080 --> 28:44.520
Okay, asshole.

28:44.640 --> 28:46.280
Okay, stop, stop! Okay.

28:46.360 --> 28:48.680
You win.

28:48.760 --> 28:50.560
Back up.

28:50.680 --> 28:53.440
Against the wall, now!

28:53.560 --> 28:54.760
I was just trying to help.

28:56.720 --> 28:58.000
Who is it up there?

28:58.080 --> 28:59.880
How the hell should I know, huh?

28:59.960 --> 29:02.320
Some backwoods hillbilly.
Will you just shoot him?

29:04.520 --> 29:06.960
Fuck.

29:13.320 --> 29:14.560
Just shoot him.

29:16.320 --> 29:18.560
There's nothing here.

29:18.680 --> 29:21.640
-What is this?
-A tranquilizer.

29:21.760 --> 29:23.760
-This is useless.
-Just shoot the fucker!

29:27.520 --> 29:29.560
You look trapped, huh?

29:29.680 --> 29:32.080
Well, fucking improvise
something.

29:32.200 --> 29:35.240
I plan, I don't improvise.

29:35.400 --> 29:37.600
Of course.

29:37.720 --> 29:39.160
Because you never had to.

29:39.240 --> 29:41.000
Look, will you just shoot him?

29:43.480 --> 29:44.800
What the fuck are you doing?

29:47.440 --> 29:49.520
That door's not gonna hold forever.

30:17.800 --> 30:18.800
What is it?

30:18.960 --> 30:20.040
Hey!

30:20.160 --> 30:21.560
Hey!

30:38.240 --> 30:39.960
Help!

30:40.080 --> 30:41.440
Stop!

30:44.440 --> 30:46.720
Just shoot the fucker!

30:46.840 --> 30:48.000
Shoot him!

30:50.440 --> 30:51.840
If I die, you die!

31:04.320 --> 31:05.920
You fucking kill him.

31:13.080 --> 31:15.160
No, no, no.

31:15.280 --> 31:16.400
No.

31:18.120 --> 31:19.600
Come on!

31:24.840 --> 31:26.960
You have one left.

31:27.040 --> 31:28.800
Give me that fucking glove.

31:32.160 --> 31:34.560
You impress me at every turn.

31:34.680 --> 31:36.800
Take me to the snowmobile.

31:50.840 --> 31:52.640
Who was that, huh?

31:55.040 --> 31:56.880
Now, you shut up.

32:02.440 --> 32:03.800
Oh, God!

32:03.920 --> 32:06.880
Fuck.

32:09.640 --> 32:10.960
Keep moving.

32:12.000 --> 32:13.920
We gotta deal with this leg.

32:13.960 --> 32:15.360
I don't care about it.

32:15.480 --> 32:18.640
Look, I'm not gonna make it
to the snowmobile, alright?

32:18.720 --> 32:19.720
Alright, the bleeding's
not gonna stop

32:19.800 --> 32:20.800
from all the fucking walking.

32:20.880 --> 32:22.680
Fuck you and fuck your leg.

32:22.800 --> 32:23.960
Come on!

32:25.960 --> 32:27.160
Do it.

32:27.280 --> 32:30.000
I'd rather go quick
than sit here and bleed out.

32:32.000 --> 32:34.760
Go on, pull it.

32:38.680 --> 32:39.960
That's what I thought.

32:40.040 --> 32:42.240
That big bastard's gonna wake up
any second.

32:42.360 --> 32:44.720
And he's gonna see
our very obvious tracks

32:44.840 --> 32:47.200
and he's gonna be looking
for revenge.

32:47.280 --> 32:49.760
That was a dumbass decision
you made not to finish him off.

32:49.840 --> 32:51.880
Dumbass.

32:54.600 --> 32:56.560
We're gonna move a lot faster

32:56.680 --> 32:59.680
if... if I'm not coming apart
at the seams, right?

32:59.800 --> 33:02.720
I got a first-aid kit
and it's right in the backpack.

33:02.840 --> 33:04.200
Fuck.

33:04.320 --> 33:05.720
Fuck, fuck.

33:07.680 --> 33:09.280
Fuck!

33:11.720 --> 33:12.920
You want me to sit down?

33:13.000 --> 33:17.520
Face down on your stomach
on to your arms.

33:17.640 --> 33:19.000
Do it!

33:21.880 --> 33:24.440
Oh, okay.

33:26.240 --> 33:27.560
This is smart.

33:27.640 --> 33:28.640
Yeah.

33:34.080 --> 33:36.880
-Don't move.
-Oh, that fucking hurts.

33:38.920 --> 33:40.240
Pretty ironic, huh?

33:41.600 --> 33:42.880
You saving me.

33:44.680 --> 33:45.880
I'm saving me.

33:51.480 --> 33:54.840
Yeah, here, pour a little
of that tequila on the wound

33:54.960 --> 33:57.320
and then a little into my mug
right here.

34:00.240 --> 34:01.920
Just a little taste
for the pain.

34:03.240 --> 34:05.480
Shut up.

34:08.000 --> 34:09.040
I guess I'll be fine.

34:09.120 --> 34:10.560
Don't move.

34:19.440 --> 34:21.040
I know who you are.

34:23.320 --> 34:26.560
You're that guy
at the barbecue king.

34:26.680 --> 34:28.960
King's Castle Barbecue, yeah.

34:29.080 --> 34:30.400
Buddy King.

34:30.560 --> 34:32.800
It's nice to, uh, meet you.

34:33.880 --> 34:35.600
You have like a hundred restaurants.

34:35.720 --> 34:40.040
155 restaurants
around the world.

34:40.120 --> 34:42.480
Your restaurant, it's people,

34:42.600 --> 34:43.840
isn't it, the barbecue?

34:43.960 --> 34:48.320
No, I don't serve human flesh
in my restaurants.

34:48.440 --> 34:51.600
I'm an elite sportsman,
not a cannibal.

34:53.400 --> 34:55.080
Well, I did eat that one guy.

34:55.160 --> 34:57.000
That was a long time ago,
it was really...

34:57.080 --> 34:59.240
It was really more
of a bucket list kinda thing.

34:59.360 --> 35:01.920
- Shut up!
- Ow!

35:04.120 --> 35:06.000
Done.

35:06.120 --> 35:07.720
-Don't move.
-Yeah.

35:10.440 --> 35:12.040
Don't move!

35:17.080 --> 35:18.360
All right, stand up.

35:21.920 --> 35:23.440
How did you get me here?

35:26.840 --> 35:28.160
Tell me the truth.

35:28.320 --> 35:31.200
Like I said,
first on a snowmobile

35:31.360 --> 35:32.800
and a sled
the rest of the way.

35:32.920 --> 35:35.520
-Before that.
-You mean...

35:35.640 --> 35:37.360
From my home.

35:37.480 --> 35:40.480
I spent a couple of months
learning your routine.

35:40.600 --> 35:42.240
You wake up, you put on
workout clothes,

35:42.360 --> 35:44.160
you grab a few bites of granola,

35:44.280 --> 35:45.520
you hop
on your fancy spinning bike,

35:45.680 --> 35:46.800
you go take a shower.

35:48.000 --> 35:50.080
Then you get dressed.

35:50.160 --> 35:51.560
Sometimes,
you don't get dressed.

35:51.640 --> 35:53.080
You work from home,
you cook for yourself,

35:53.160 --> 35:54.320
you watch TV at night.

36:01.360 --> 36:03.920
How did you get me here?

36:04.040 --> 36:06.120
You rarely leave your house
at night.

36:06.200 --> 36:09.920
The occasional, unpredictable
night-out with your girlfriends.

36:11.640 --> 36:13.840
Or when you take
your garbage out.

36:13.960 --> 36:16.200
Sunday nights, 9:05.

36:16.360 --> 36:17.880
In your purple robe.

36:18.800 --> 36:21.560
Then in the middle of the night,
I went into your bedroom,

36:21.720 --> 36:22.920
gave you a shot.

36:24.200 --> 36:25.920
A shot of what?

36:26.040 --> 36:27.840
Fentanyl and heroin.

36:27.920 --> 36:29.640
That tranquilizer
from the basement?

36:34.560 --> 36:35.640
Why did you undress me?

36:42.040 --> 36:44.320
Ow, oh.

36:44.480 --> 36:45.880
Get up!

36:46.040 --> 36:48.800
Take me
to the fucking snowmobile.

36:58.520 --> 37:00.000
Right now.

37:00.120 --> 37:01.360
Sure.

37:03.080 --> 37:04.600
Don't forget the bag.

37:06.080 --> 37:07.360
Oh.

37:15.600 --> 37:16.880
Hey.

37:19.760 --> 37:21.080
What is this?

37:21.200 --> 37:22.400
I keep seeing them.

37:44.080 --> 37:46.080
No idea.

37:46.240 --> 37:48.080
You want to freeze
or you wanna walk?

38:05.360 --> 38:09.960
I do a lot of research
so I can learn everything I can

38:10.040 --> 38:11.280
about my guests that come here.

38:11.320 --> 38:13.200
