1:02:44.800 --> 1:02:46.400
The whole story.

1:02:51.240 --> 1:02:56.920
I was at my mailbox
when a delivery van pulled up.

1:02:57.040 --> 1:03:02.200
Mmm, he hopped out of the van
and said, "Good timing."

1:03:02.360 --> 1:03:05.120
Then slid the side door open.

1:03:07.800 --> 1:03:09.760
"Your package is in here
somewhere."

1:03:11.240 --> 1:03:13.040
I had to reach up for it.

1:03:14.960 --> 1:03:16.760
And in one second...

1:03:18.440 --> 1:03:20.880
someone grabbed me
and pulled me inside.

1:03:24.240 --> 1:03:29.200
Next thing I remember,
I was waking up in the basement.

1:03:30.560 --> 1:03:32.840
It was hot down there.

1:03:33.000 --> 1:03:34.400
Dark, no windows.

1:03:36.320 --> 1:03:39.080
When he'd come down uh,

1:03:39.200 --> 1:03:45.000
to either bring food
or... rape me...

1:03:46.960 --> 1:03:50.640
...he opened the door
at the top of the stairs,

1:03:50.800 --> 1:03:52.960
and for one second, this...

1:03:55.160 --> 1:03:58.600
bright light from above

1:03:59.800 --> 1:04:00.840
shined down.

1:04:02.200 --> 1:04:03.800
Ah.

1:04:03.880 --> 1:04:05.720
Oh, but then,

1:04:05.840 --> 1:04:09.800
he'd lock the door behind him
and came down.

1:04:14.720 --> 1:04:15.840
Hmm.

1:04:19.360 --> 1:04:21.640
One time,
he didn't lock the door.

1:04:21.760 --> 1:04:24.880
He just went to get something
from the other corner

1:04:25.000 --> 1:04:30.160
of the basement
and the bright light

1:04:30.320 --> 1:04:32.640
just lit up the stairs.

1:04:34.320 --> 1:04:36.440
I thought I could get out.

1:04:39.280 --> 1:04:40.320
So, I ran.

1:04:41.600 --> 1:04:42.680
And I got out.

1:04:46.520 --> 1:04:47.560
What, that's it?

1:04:51.400 --> 1:04:55.440
I told you,
there were no fancy tricks,

1:04:55.600 --> 1:04:57.280
no ninja skills.

1:04:57.400 --> 1:04:58.880
He made a dumbass mistake.

1:05:02.280 --> 1:05:04.720
What happened?

1:05:15.920 --> 1:05:16.920
He...

1:05:18.640 --> 1:05:19.800
He brought down...

1:05:21.560 --> 1:05:24.480
he brought down a young girl.

1:05:24.600 --> 1:05:26.440
She was only 17.

1:05:27.720 --> 1:05:28.840
She was...

1:05:31.640 --> 1:05:36.280
She was beautiful,
kind, smart...

1:05:38.320 --> 1:05:39.640
and scared.

1:05:45.120 --> 1:05:46.400
It...

1:05:47.560 --> 1:05:49.520
It didn't matter
what he did to me.

1:05:49.640 --> 1:05:51.160
Just...

1:05:52.520 --> 1:05:54.640
Just it didn't matter.

1:05:54.760 --> 1:05:58.080
It was listening to him
doing that to her.

1:06:00.840 --> 1:06:02.640
Her crying.

1:06:04.080 --> 1:06:06.440
Her screaming.

1:06:06.560 --> 1:06:09.840
I knew I had to get us
out of there.

1:06:09.960 --> 1:06:12.400
I felt so responsible for her.

1:06:12.520 --> 1:06:15.200
I had to get her out of there.

1:06:18.440 --> 1:06:21.240
So, the day
he left the door open...

1:06:23.280 --> 1:06:28.080
and the light just shone down,
I yelled.

1:06:29.400 --> 1:06:31.040
"Run!"

1:06:32.800 --> 1:06:34.040
And we ran.

1:06:35.280 --> 1:06:36.920
I made it out of the house.

1:06:38.640 --> 1:06:39.920
She didn't.

1:06:41.200 --> 1:06:45.320
I hear her screams every day.

1:06:50.440 --> 1:06:52.520
We both killed someone
we didn't want to.

1:06:55.520 --> 1:06:56.840
We're the same.

1:07:01.720 --> 1:07:03.080
Okay.

1:07:03.200 --> 1:07:04.880
Hey, hey, hey, hey.

1:07:05.000 --> 1:07:06.600
Alright, I respect that you
tried that.

1:07:11.520 --> 1:07:13.040
I appreciate you telling me
your story.

1:07:15.360 --> 1:07:16.760
I feel really connected to you
right now.

1:07:16.840 --> 1:07:17.760
I don't know.
I don't wanna sound corny,

1:07:17.920 --> 1:07:19.560
but...

1:07:19.680 --> 1:07:21.640
I do wish the day could go on
forever.

1:07:24.040 --> 1:07:26.240
But all things come to an end,
so...

1:07:32.800 --> 1:07:34.040
Let's go.

1:07:37.920 --> 1:07:40.040
What?

1:07:40.160 --> 1:07:43.000
It's only fair you get to see
the finish line.

1:07:43.120 --> 1:07:45.080
It's the way
it's supposed to be.

1:07:45.160 --> 1:07:46.400
Go on.

1:07:46.560 --> 1:07:49.080
