as dark as they seem right now.

1:08:47.480 --> 1:08:48.880
All this?

1:08:49.000 --> 1:08:50.920
This whole journey?

1:08:51.040 --> 1:08:52.120
You...

1:08:52.240 --> 1:08:54.120
