1:09:43.920 --> 1:09:45.280
Yeah, well, good for you,
imbecile.

1:09:45.400 --> 1:09:46.920
We... hey, will you just
hear me out?

1:09:49.000 --> 1:09:50.920
We both
got our baggage, right?

1:09:51.280 --> 1:09:52.880
